---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="SaaS Product Development | Intelio - Build Scalable Recurring Revenue Products" description="Transform your service delivery into a scalable SaaS product. Build once, deploy to thousands. Create recurring revenue and defensible competitive advantage.">
<main class="bg-white">
  <!-- ENHANCED HERO SECTION -->
  <section class="relative min-h-[90vh] flex items-center overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-900 via-slate-900 to-gray-900">
    <!-- Video Background -->
    <video 
      autoplay 
      loop 
      muted 
      playsinline
      class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover opacity-40"
    >
      <source src="/logos/Cinematic_Finance_Animation_Generation (1).mp4" type="video/mp4">
    </video>
    
    <!-- Gradient Overlay -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-gray-900/95 via-gray-900/80 to-gray-900/60 z-[1]"></div>
    
    <!-- Subtle noise texture -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-[0.02] mix-blend-overlay z-[2]" style="background-image: url('data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg width=\'100\' height=\'100\' xmlns=\'http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\'%3E%3Cfilter id=\'noise\'%3E%3CfeTurbulence type=\'fractalNoise\' baseFrequency=\'0.9\' numOctaves=\'4\'/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width=\'100%25\' height=\'100%25\' filter=\'url(%23noise)\'/%3E%3C/svg%3E');"></div>

    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 py-24 w-full">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <!-- Badge -->
        <div class="mb-6">
          <span class="text-blue-400 text-sm font-bold tracking-[0.2em] uppercase">
            SaaS Development
          </span>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Headline -->
        <h1 class="text-5xl lg:text-7xl font-bold text-white leading-[1.1] mb-6 tracking-tight">
          SaaS Product Development
        </h1>
        
        <!-- Subtitle -->
        <p class="text-xl lg:text-2xl text-gray-200 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
          Build once. Scale to thousands. Transform service delivery into recurring revenue.
        </p>
        
        <!-- Description -->
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-300 mb-10 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
          You've solved a problem for one client exceptionally well. Now you're solving the same problem for another client. And another. Building the same system repeatedly. Same work. Same cost. Same team needed for each client.<br><br>That's a services business. It doesn't scale revenue. It doesn't create leverage. It doesn't create value that compounds.<br><br>What if you productized that solution? Built it once, deployed to many. Scaled revenue without scaling headcount. Turned expertise into a defensible, scalable asset.<br><br>That's the SaaS opportunity. We help you build it.
        </p>
        
        <!-- CTAs -->
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
          <a href="#what-we-build" class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-4 bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-500 text-white text-lg font-semibold rounded-xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300">
            Explore SaaS Development
            <svg class="ml-2 w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
            </svg>
          </a>
          <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-4 border-2 border-white/30 hover:border-white/60 text-white text-lg font-semibold rounded-xl hover:bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm transition-all duration-300">
            Schedule SaaS Strategy Call
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Scroll indicator -->
    <div class="absolute bottom-8 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 z-10 animate-bounce">
      <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white/50" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 14l-7 7m0 0l-7-7m7 7V3"></path>
      </svg>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CREDIBILITY BAR -->
  <section class="py-12 px-6 bg-white border-b border-gray-100">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-6">
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 font-medium">Trusted by operations leaders at:</p>
        <!-- Client Logos - Infinite Scroll -->
        <div class="logo-marquee-container w-full">
          <div class="logo-marquee-track">
            <!-- First set of logos -->
            <div class="logo-marquee-item">
              <img src="/logos/Newmark-logo.png" alt="Newmark" class="logo-marquee-img" onerror="this.style.display='none'; this.nextElementSibling.style.display='block';">
              <span class="text-gray-400 font-medium" style="display:none;">Newmark</span>
            </div>
            <div class="logo-marquee-item">
              <img src="/logos/hhp-grey-logo.png" alt="HHP" class="logo-marquee-img" onerror="this.style.display='none'; this.nextElementSibling.style.display='block';">
              <span class="text-gray-400 font-medium" style="display:none;">HHP</span>
            </div>
            <div class="logo-marquee-item">
              <img src="/logos/alliance-resource.png" alt="Alliance Resource Partners" class="logo-marquee-img" onerror="this.style.display='none'; this.nextElementSibling.style.display='block';">
              <span class="text-gray-400 font-medium text-sm" style="display:none;">Alliance Resource Partners</span>
            </div>
            <div class="logo-marquee-item">
              <img src="/logos/manhattan-construction-logo.png" alt="Manhattan Construction" class="logo-marquee-img" onerror="this.style.display='none'; this.nextElementSibling.style.display='block';">
              <span class="text-gray-400 font-medium text-sm" style="display:none;">Manhattan Construction</span>
            </div>
            <div class="logo-marquee-item">
              <img src="/logos/brain-body-soul-logo.png" alt="Brain Body Soul" class="logo-marquee-img" onerror="this.style.display='none'; this.nextElementSibling.style.display='block';">
              <span class="text-gray-400 font-medium text-sm" style="display:none;">Brain Body Soul</span>
            </div>
            <div class="logo-marquee-item">
              <img src="/logos/JLL-Logo.png" alt="JLL" class="logo-marquee-img" onerror="this.style.display='none'; this.nextElementSibling.style.display='block';">
              <span class="text-gray-400 font-medium" style="display:none;">JLL</span>
            </div>
            <div class="logo-marquee-item">
              <img src="/logos/CB logo.png" alt="CB" class="logo-marquee-img" onerror="this.style.display='none'; this.nextElementSibling.style.display='block';">
              <span class="text-gray-400 font-medium" style="display:none;">CB</span>
            </div>
            <!-- Duplicate set for seamless loop -->
            <div class="logo-marquee-item">
              <img src="/logos/Newmark-logo.png" alt="Newmark" class="logo-marquee-img" onerror="this.style.display='none'; this.nextElementSibling.style.display='block';">
              <span class="text-gray-400 font-medium" style="display:none;">Newmark</span>
            </div>
            <div class="logo-marquee-item">
              <img src="/logos/hhp-grey-logo.png" alt="HHP" class="logo-marquee-img" onerror="this.style.display='none'; this.nextElementSibling.style.display='block';">
              <span class="text-gray-400 font-medium" style="display:none;">HHP</span>
            </div>
            <div class="logo-marquee-item">
              <img src="/logos/alliance-resource.png" alt="Alliance Resource Partners" class="logo-marquee-img" onerror="this.style.display='none'; this.nextElementSibling.style.display='block';">
              <span class="text-gray-400 font-medium text-sm" style="display:none;">Alliance Resource Partners</span>
            </div>
            <div class="logo-marquee-item">
              <img src="/logos/manhattan-construction-logo.png" alt="Manhattan Construction" class="logo-marquee-img" onerror="this.style.display='none'; this.nextElementSibling.style.display='block';">
              <span class="text-gray-400 font-medium text-sm" style="display:none;">Manhattan Construction</span>
            </div>
            <div class="logo-marquee-item">
              <img src="/logos/brain-body-soul-logo.png" alt="Brain Body Soul" class="logo-marquee-img" onerror="this.style.display='none'; this.nextElementSibling.style.display='block';">
              <span class="text-gray-400 font-medium text-sm" style="display:none;">Brain Body Soul</span>
            </div>
            <div class="logo-marquee-item">
              <img src="/logos/JLL-Logo.png" alt="JLL" class="logo-marquee-img" onerror="this.style.display='none'; this.nextElementSibling.style.display='block';">
              <span class="text-gray-400 font-medium" style="display:none;">JLL</span>
            </div>
            <div class="logo-marquee-item">
              <img src="/logos/CB logo.png" alt="CB" class="logo-marquee-img" onerror="this.style.display='none'; this.nextElementSibling.style.display='block';">
              <span class="text-gray-400 font-medium" style="display:none;">CB</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PROBLEM SECTION -->
  <section class="problem-section py-20 md:py-24 px-6 bg-white relative">
    <!-- Left Accent Line (Animated) -->
    <div class="problem-accent-line absolute left-0 top-0 w-1 bg-blue-600 rounded-full z-10"></div>
    
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto relative z-10">
      <div class="mb-16 scroll-fade-in">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6 inline-block pb-4 border-b-4 border-blue-600">
          Why Service Delivery Models Break at Scale
        </h2>
        <p class="text-base text-gray-600 max-w-3xl leading-relaxed mt-6 mb-12">
          You've solved it for 3 clients. Each took 6 weeks. Each made money. Now you want to scale. Here's what happens:
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-10 relative pl-8">
        <!-- Problem 1 -->
        <div class="problem-card bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-blue-50/30 rounded-lg p-8 border-t-4 border-l-4 border-blue-600 border-r border-b border-gray-200 hover:border-blue-500 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 scroll-fade-in">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="problem-icon flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-blue-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 7h12m0 0l-4-4m4 4l-4 4m0 6H4m0 0l4 4m-4-4l4-4"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1">
              <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-blue-600 mb-3">Margins Disappear Into Headcount</h3>
              <p class="text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                New client = new team. Revenue scales. Profit doesn't.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Problem 2 -->
        <div class="problem-card bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-blue-50/30 rounded-lg p-8 border-t-4 border-l-4 border-blue-600 border-r border-b border-gray-200 hover:border-blue-500 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 scroll-fade-in">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="problem-icon flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-blue-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6V4m0 2a2 2 0 100 4m0-4a2 2 0 110 4m-6 8a2 2 0 100-4m0 4a2 2 0 110-4m0 4v2m0-6V4m6 6v10m6-2a2 2 0 100-4m0 4a2 2 0 110-4m0 4v2m0-6V4"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1">
              <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-blue-600 mb-3">Scaling = Job Factory</h3>
              <p class="text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                Revenue ceiling = team size × projects per person. Capped upside.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Problem 3 -->
        <div class="problem-card bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-blue-50/30 rounded-lg p-8 border-t-4 border-l-4 border-blue-600 border-r border-b border-gray-200 hover:border-blue-500 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 scroll-fade-in">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="problem-icon flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-blue-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M18.364 18.364A9 9 0 005.636 5.636m12.728 12.728A9 9 0 015.636 5.636m12.728 12.728L5.636 5.636"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1">
              <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-blue-600 mb-3">Dependent on People, Not Process</h3>
              <p class="text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                One person leaves = crisis. Managing people, not building capability.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Problem 4 -->
        <div class="problem-card bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-blue-50/30 rounded-lg p-8 border-t-4 border-l-4 border-blue-600 border-r border-b border-gray-200 hover:border-blue-500 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 scroll-fade-in">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="problem-icon flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-blue-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 15v2m-6 4h12a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm10-10V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4h8z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1">
              <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-blue-600 mb-3">Clients Can Leave Easily</h3>
              <p class="text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                6-week implementations. Not sticky. Lifetime value = contract length.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Problem 5 -->
        <div class="problem-card bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-blue-50/30 rounded-lg p-8 border-t-4 border-l-4 border-blue-600 border-r border-b border-gray-200 hover:border-blue-500 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 scroll-fade-in">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="problem-icon flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-blue-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7h8m0 0v8m0-8l-8 8-4-4-6 6"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1">
              <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-blue-600 mb-3">Expertise Is Bottlenecked</h3>
              <p class="text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                One expert = one constraint. Can't scale faster than they work.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Problem 6 -->
        <div class="problem-card bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-blue-50/30 rounded-lg p-8 border-t-4 border-l-4 border-blue-600 border-r border-b border-gray-200 hover:border-blue-500 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 scroll-fade-in">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="problem-icon flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-blue-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1">
              <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-blue-600 mb-3">You Hit the Ceiling</h3>
              <p class="text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                $2–$5M revenue cap. Lifestyle business. No exit. No upside.<br><br><strong>Unless you productize.</strong>
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHAT WE BUILD SECTION -->
  <section id="what-we-build" class="py-20 md:py-24 px-6 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
          Turn Expertise Into a Scalable Product
        </h2>
        <div class="w-24 h-1 bg-blue-600 mx-auto mb-6"></div>
        <p class="text-base text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
          Productization transforms a service into an asset. Instead of trading time for money, you build once and deploy repeatedly. Revenue scales. Headcount doesn't. Profit multiplies.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="capability-cards-pyramid grid grid-cols-3 gap-6 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <!-- Card 1: Row 1 - Centered -->
        <div class="capability-card capability-card-pyramid-1 col-start-2 bg-gradient-to-b from-white to-gray-50 rounded-xl p-10 border-t-2 border-blue-600 border-r border-b border-l border-gray-200 hover:border-blue-500 hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 scroll-fade-in-stagger" style="animation-delay: 0ms;">
          <div class="relative mb-6">
            <div class="capability-badge absolute -top-2 -right-2 w-8 h-8 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-bold">01</div>
            <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-100 to-blue-50 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center shadow-md hover:rotate-6 transition-transform duration-300">
              <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 7v10c0 2.21 3.582 4 8 4s8-1.79 8-4V7M4 7c0 2.21 3.582 4 8 4s8-1.79 8-4M4 7c0-2.21 3.582-4 8-4s8 1.79 8 4m0 5c0 2.21-3.582 4-8 4s-8-1.79-8-4"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="h-0.5 w-12 bg-gray-200 mb-4"></div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-blue-600 mb-3">Reusable Systems. Configurable for Each Customer.</h3>
          <p class="text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            Your custom solution for Client A has components that apply to Client B. And Client C. And every other client with that problem. We identify the reusable core and build configurability around it. Vertical-specific workflows. White-label options. Tenant-specific customization. One system serves many clients, each with their specific needs.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Card 2: Row 2 - Left -->
        <div class="capability-card capability-card-pyramid-2 col-start-1 bg-gradient-to-b from-white to-gray-50 rounded-xl p-10 border-t-2 border-blue-600 border-r border-b border-l border-gray-200 hover:border-blue-500 hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 scroll-fade-in-stagger" style="animation-delay: 100ms;">
          <div class="relative mb-6">
            <div class="capability-badge absolute -top-2 -right-2 w-8 h-8 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-bold">02</div>
            <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-100 to-blue-50 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center shadow-md hover:rotate-6 transition-transform duration-300">
              <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="h-0.5 w-12 bg-gray-200 mb-4"></div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-blue-600 mb-3">Multi-Tenant Infrastructure</h3>
          <p class="text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            Running one system per customer means one database per customer, one server per customer, one support instance per customer. That's expensive at scale. Multi-tenant architecture means one system serves 100 customers, with data isolation, per-tenant configuration, and independent scaling. Same infrastructure cost serves 100x the revenue.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Card 3: Row 2 - Right -->
        <div class="capability-card capability-card-pyramid-3 col-start-3 bg-gradient-to-b from-white to-gray-50 rounded-xl p-10 border-t-2 border-blue-600 border-r border-b border-l border-gray-200 hover:border-blue-500 hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 scroll-fade-in-stagger" style="animation-delay: 200ms;">
          <div class="relative mb-6">
            <div class="capability-badge absolute -top-2 -right-2 w-8 h-8 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-bold">03</div>
            <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-100 to-blue-50 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center shadow-md hover:rotate-6 transition-transform duration-300">
              <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 17V7m0 10a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2V7a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2m0 10a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 7a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2m0 10V7m0 10a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2a2 2 0 00-2 2"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="h-0.5 w-12 bg-gray-200 mb-4"></div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-blue-600 mb-3">Automated Deployment</h3>
          <p class="text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            Right now, each new client takes 6 weeks to implement. That's 6 weeks of team time. 6 weeks of consulting cost. 6 weeks before you make money. With productization, new customers can be up and running in 1 week. Mostly automated. Your team does onboarding and customization, not rearchitecting.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Card 4: Row 3 - Left -->
        <div class="capability-card capability-card-pyramid-4 col-start-1 bg-gradient-to-b from-white to-gray-50 rounded-xl p-10 border-t-2 border-blue-600 border-r border-b border-l border-gray-200 hover:border-blue-500 hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 scroll-fade-in-stagger" style="animation-delay: 300ms;">
          <div class="relative mb-6">
            <div class="capability-badge absolute -top-2 -right-2 w-8 h-8 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-bold">04</div>
            <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-100 to-blue-50 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center shadow-md hover:rotate-6 transition-transform duration-300">
              <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M11 4a2 2 0 114 0v1a1 1 0 001 1h3a1 1 0 011 1v3a1 1 0 01-1 1h-1a2 2 0 100 4h1a1 1 0 011 1v3a1 1 0 01-1 1h-3a1 1 0 01-1-1v-1a2 2 0 10-4 0v1a1 1 0 01-1 1H7a1 1 0 01-1-1v-3a1 1 0 00-1-1H4a2 2 0 110-4h1a1 1 0 001-1V7a1 1 0 011-1h3a1 1 0 001-1V4z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>
